{
  "title": "CentOS 服务器注意事项",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">安装 CentOS 分区设置, 10G 大小足够</p><pre class=\"sql hljs\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; overflow: auto; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; padding: 1em; margin-top: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 1.5em; line-height: 1.3; word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(101, 123, 131); background-color: rgb(246, 246, 246); border: none; border-top-left-radius: 3px; border-top-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-right-radius: 3px; border-bottom-left-radius: 3px; background-image: url(https://sf-static.b0.upaiyun.com/v-57aafee9/global/img/blueprint.png); background-size: 30px, 30px; max-height: 35em; position: relative;\"><code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 1em; color: inherit; border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; white-space: inherit; background-image: none; overflow-wrap: normal;\">    <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(147, 161, 161);\">---  Swap   交换分区   swap 格式  不要超过2000M</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(147, 161, 161);\">---  Boot   /boot     Ext4 格式     200M ~ 500M </span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(147, 161, 161);\">---  /          /     Ext4 格式    根目录  所有空间</span>\n</code></pre><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">在图形界面右键，选择“终端”，就可以进入命令行模式</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">虚拟机安装网络采用默认的 Nat 模式。<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">本机测试 IP 是 192.168.2.128</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Linux 严格区分大小写，命令全部是小写, 如果用 SecureCrt 连接不上远程 CentOS,&nbsp;<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">请确保进入桌面环境右下角的网络连接已经打开，用root账号登录，&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">netstat -atp 查看端口号 22是否有开启<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">ifconfig 查看主机IP地址&nbsp;&nbsp;<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">都OK 的话，打开 SecureCrt 重新连接 ok</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">务必学会 vi 编辑器<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Shell 与 Shell Script 学习</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">Ctrl + Alt + F1 ~ F6 切换到终端<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ctrl + Alt + F7 切换到图形界面<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">startx 启动到图形界面</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">系统运行级别</span><br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">0、关机<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1、单用户,root用<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2、不完全多用户，不含NetworkFileService 服务<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3、完全多用户<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4、未分配<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">5、图形界面<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">6、重启<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">.</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">CentOS 7 设置开机直接进入命令行界面</span></p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">inittab文件已经不被使用，现在CentOS7使用systemd作为新的init系统，默认有两个主要的target：<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">multi-user.target： 相当于runlevel 3[命令行界面]，<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">graphical.target： 相当于runlevel 5[图形界面]&nbsp;</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">我这里要将CentOS7开机默认进入命令行界面，则运行命令：<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"># ln -sf /lib/systemd/system/<code class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Source Code Pro', Consolas, Menlo, Monaco, 'Courier New', monospace; font-size: 0.93em; color: rgb(199, 37, 78); background-color: rgb(249, 242, 244); padding: 2px 4px;\">multi-user.target</code>&nbsp;/etc/systemd/system/default.target</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">如果要换回图形界面启动，用 graphical.target 替换上行红色部分代码</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\">查看当前默认的模式：<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">systemctl get-default 注意是小写的l(L)</p><p class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'Microsoft Yahei', sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">服务器管理和维护建议</span><br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">1、远程服务器不允许关机，只能重启<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">2、重启时应该关闭服务<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">3、不要在服务器访问高峰运行高负载命令(全盘复制、扫描、杀毒、压缩解压缩等)<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">4、远程配置防火墙时不要把自己提出服务器<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">5、指定合理的密码规范并定期更新<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">6、合理分配权限，用户权限够用就好，系统启动服务越少越好<br class=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">7、定期备份重要数据和日志</p>"
    }
  ]
}